<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ke<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi> riva<unclear>ṉ</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>makku yāṇṭu 5 Āvatu <hi rend="grantha">kumga</hi> nā<unclear>ya</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṟu k<hi rend="grantha">u</hi> ṉṟakūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha">m</hi> ci<unclear>ṟu</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>paḻuvūr <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi> yom viṟṟa Ūrnila vi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>laiyāvaṇam Āṭikaḷ<note n="285-1">Read aṭikaḷ.</note>paḻuveṭṭaraiyarma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṟavaṉ kaṇṭaṉārkku viṟṟukkuṭutta Ūrāva
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tu kuṉṟakkūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi> yam cemputaṟkuṭi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>c cemputaṟkuṭi nilattukku kiḻpāṟ kellai tā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>pameṉṟu per collappaṭukiṉṟa Ūrnilattu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kkum kaṭalaikuṭi Ūrnilattukku mekku teṉpā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṟ kellai Ikkaṭalaikuṭi Ū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>nilattukkum kūṉappāṭi
<lb n="12"/>Ūrnilattukkum melpāṟ kellai Ik
<lb n="13" break="no"/>kūḷappāṭi Ūrnilattukkum Uṟat tū
<lb n="14" break="no"/>r Ūrnilattukkum kiḻakku vaṭapāṟ ke
<lb n="15" break="no"/>llai Ivvuṟattūr Ūrnilattukkum
<lb n="16"/><unclear>tā</unclear>pamākiya Ūrnilattukkum
<lb n="17"/>teṟku Ivvicaitta perunāṉ ke
<lb n="18" break="no"/>llaiyu<supplied reason="omitted">ḷ</supplied> ḷaka<supplied reason="omitted">p</supplied>paṭṭa nilam vaḷaiyiṟcuṟṟu
<lb n="19" break="no"/>muṟṟu muṇṇila moḻiviṉṟiye ni
<lb n="20" break="no"/>rnilamum puṉceyum meṉceyyu
<lb n="21" break="no"/>m kiṇaṟum kuḷamuṅ koṭṭakāramum maṉ
<lb n="22" break="no"/>ṟuṅ kaṉṟumey pāḻum puṟṟun teṟ<unclear>ṟi</unclear>
<lb n="23" break="no"/>yum cuṭukāṭum Uṭpaṭa maṟṟu mep
<lb n="24" break="no"/>perppaṭṭa nilamum Innila meḻun
<lb n="25" break="no"/>ta maramum marappayaṉum maṟṟu mu
<lb n="26" break="no"/>ṭumpoṭi yāmai tava<supplied reason="omitted">ḻ</supplied>nta te
<lb n="27" break="no"/>pperppaṭṭatum nāṅkaḷ Ic
<lb n="28" break="no"/>cempūtakkuṭi <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi> yār <unclear>pak</unclear><note n="285-2">The rest of the inscription cannot be traced: it is not continued on the sides or at bottom.</note> 
